com.apple.eawt

Packages that use com.apple.eawt
com.apple.eawt Provides classes for integrating Java applications with the native application environment. 
 

Classes in com.apple.eawt used by com.apple.eawt
Application
          The Application class allows you to integrate your Java code with the native Mac OS X application environment.
ApplicationEvent
          The class of events sent to ApplicationListener callbacks.
ApplicationListener
          The listener interface for receiving ApplicationEvents.
